I bet you if they came out and said &quot;we're going to make EQ a fully interactive virtual environment complete with 3D goggles and sensory equipment, photo-realistic graphics, complete voice/movment interface at no extra charge to you, the response would be: &quot;meh, I'd get goggle lines on my face&quot;.<br>
