As for the 9th spell gem...woot! I'm always looking for one more song.  I won't give up my ornate greaves just because I don't want to have to devote a song gem to selos (that and I like the 1 second cast...another item I wish was inventory clickable.)<br>
<br>
More spell slots will be nice, but not as necessary.  I rarely have to click effects off, and when I do it's *normally* easy to decide.  Not bad though.<br>
<br>
Overall the expansion sounds solid enough, depending on the results of the content.<br>
